{"tid":1459183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益］機場和你飛英文口號都好重要架","createTime":"2019-08-12T16:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T08:47:02.000Z","uid":210122,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ee1998a953036cd6ea3bc121496c00f2828fd4da","tid":1459183,"uid":210122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:26:36.000Z","msg":"經過812 見到大家都好用力嗌 <span style=\"color: blue;\">黑警還眼 </span> <strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港警察 知法犯法</span></strong> <span style=\"color: purple;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span><br />\n但見到旅客嘅表情大多數厭惡、捂住耳仔。<br />\n呢個時候我代入左佢地嘅感受，如果我去到日本、泰國等地，我聽到佢地好嬲嬲樣咁大大聲用我唔明嘅語言叫口號 我當下應該會係困惑 只想快啲逃離現場 更唔想理你呢件事係因為啲咩引起。 相反 ， 如果我地用英文口號（雖然某啲遊客都係未必聽得明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n 但至少可以令聽得明嘅遊客了解我地究竟反緊啲乜，為啲乜出黎機場阻住佢地先（呢個係事實）<br />\n<br />\n而家綜合812經歷，有幾款係大家叫過：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. Shame on Hong Kong police</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">2. Don&rsquo;t trust the police </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">3. Free Hong Kong, Democracy Now</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">4. Stand with Hong Kong, fight for freedom</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有無其他可以帶出我地嘅主題？<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求英文版：5 demands，no one less 好似無叫過 只得文宣"},{"pid":"4b0574f5afbfd59a3951cdd26f404fe2f62fed1c","tid":1459183,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:29:00.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"b82d5ce699ce3719ad9808daeabe284be94e5eca","tid":1459183,"uid":210122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:40:52.000Z","msg":"題外話<br />\n大家聽日機場唔